Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.93,0:01:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.96,0:01:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.17,0:01:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.81,0:01:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Armin Arlert from Shiganshina District, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.88,0:01:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so? What a ridiculous name!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.22,0:01:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did your father name you that?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.26,0:01:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My grandfather did, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.18,0:01:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arlert, what did you come here to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.97,0:01:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To contribute to mankind's victory, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.14,0:01:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How commendable of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll use you as Titan bait.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.11,0:02:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Third line, face backwards!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.52,0:02:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.82,0:02:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thomas Wagner from Trost District, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.71,0:02:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.28,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thomas Wagner from Trost—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.28,0:02:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There they go again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.28,0:02:11.06,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Still no good!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.58,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Go work on it in the stables!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.58,0:02:13.41,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.60,0:02:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went through that first thing \Nwhen you were in training too, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.41,0:02:14.72,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.73,0:02:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It brings me back.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.20,0:02:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're from a pigsty—worse than cattle!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm worse than cattle, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the point of intimidating them?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.76,0:02:23.63,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.97,0:02:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a rite of passage.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.00,0:02:26.46,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.46,0:02:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You reject the you up until then,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.46,0:02:27.29,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.29,0:02:28.24,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.66,0:02:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in order to be shaped into capable \Nsoldiers, fresh from a clean slate.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.49,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Go home, right this instant!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a necessary process to accomplish that.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.49,0:02:35.15,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To devote my flesh and blood to humanity, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fourth line, face backwards!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.61,0:02:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he just skipped past that girl over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.90,0:02:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rite of passage is unnecessary for \Nthose who've already been through it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.86,0:02:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're likely to be the ones who \Nwitnessed hell two years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.96,0:02:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It shows on their faces.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.08,0:02:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, let's be off.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jean Kirstein from Trost District, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.64,0:03:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you come here to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.14,0:03:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To enlist in the Military Police Brigade \Nand live within the inner walls, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.37,0:03:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.61,0:03:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you want to live within the inner walls, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.64,0:03:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.43,0:03:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who said you could sit?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.26,0:03:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who can't succeed here won't \Nmake it into the Military Police Brigade!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.65,0:03:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you come here to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.52,0:03:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Marco Bott from Jinae Village in \NWall Rose's southern district, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.11,0:03:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've come to enlist in the Military Police Brigade, \Nand devote myself to serving the king, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.62,0:03:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all fine and well.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endeavor for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.18,0:03:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The king has no desire for your body.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're next!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.34,0:03:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Connie Springer from Ragako Village \Nin Wall Rose's southern district, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.88,0:03:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have it backwards, Connie Springer.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should've been the first thing you learned—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.96,0:04:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that salute is a symbol that openly declares \Nyour determination to offer your life.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.77,0:04:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is your heart on the right side?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.72,0:04:17.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.29,0:04:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1\b1}You{\i0\b0}, I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.60,0:04:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sasha Blouse from Dauper Village \Nin Wall Rose's southern district, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sasha Blouse,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.38,0:04:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what the hell is in your right hand?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.31,0:04:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A steamed potato, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.18,0:04:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happened to see it in\N the kitchen, so I took it, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.87,0:04:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, you {\i1\b1}stole{\i0\b0} it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.37,0:04:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you take that potato out now?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.43,0:04:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's best to eat it before it gets cold,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I decided now was the time to do so, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.61,0:05:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I still don't understand...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you eat the potato?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.64,0:05:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you asking me why people eat potatoes, sir?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.52,0:05:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This half's for you, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.17,0:05:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.88,0:05:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, the potato girl's still running.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.57,0:05:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, she's been at it for five hours.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.78,0:05:44.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she didn't seem to mind \Nthe "run till you drop" part
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.49,0:05:48.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,quite as much as being told \Nshe'd have to skip dinner, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.03,0:05:54.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dauper Village is a small village of \Nhunters deep in the mountains, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.11,0:05:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dropouts.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They opted to be transferred to reclaimed land.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's still only the first day.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The powerless have no choice but to leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.58,0:06:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Choosing to go back to picking \Nup rocks and pulling weeds...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You weren't asked to state your \Nname and birthplace or anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.80,0:06:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm from Shiganshina District, just like this guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you were there on {\i1\b1}that{\i0\b0} day, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.79,0:06:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you catch a glimpse of it? \NThe Colossus Titan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.58,0:06:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.47,0:06:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I saw everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.05,0:06:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just how big is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.84,0:06:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big enough to stick its head over the wall.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.27,0:06:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard it's big enough to straddle!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.23,0:06:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard in my village too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.81,0:06:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't quite that big.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does its face look like?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.96,0:06:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's mostly skinless and has a huge mouth.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about the Armored Titan that \Nsmashed through Wall Maria?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.92,0:07:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what people are calling it, but it \Nlooked like an average Titan to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.37,0:07:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-Then what's an average Titan like?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.93,0:07:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let's stop questioning him.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are things he'd rather not recall.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.97,0:07:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.98,0:07:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Titans really aren't that big a deal.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.58,0:07:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once we master the use of the\Nthree-dimensional maneuver device,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they won't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can finally train as a soldier.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My emotions just got the better of me earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.28,0:07:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll enlist in the Survey Corps and \Nexterminate the Titans from this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll slaughter them—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa there. You crazy?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.75,0:07:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you just say you're going \Nto enlist in the Survey Corps?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.40,0:08:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken, you're aiming to live \Nit up in the Military Police Brigade, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm an honest guy, you see.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.36,0:08:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd say I'm a lot more pleasant to be around \Nthan someone who puts on a brave face,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,despite being terrified deep down inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you implying something?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Q-Quit it, guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to dismiss your opinion.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's call it even with this.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.69,0:08:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I crossed the line too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.36,0:08:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.62,0:09:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, well, I've never seen \Nanybody like you before is all.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.55,0:09:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your black hair looks beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.34,0:09:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.67,0:09:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares? Leave me be.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.92,0:09:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're quick to act impulsively \Nwhen you get angry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.89,0:09:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That again?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.88,0:09:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't you think your hair is too long?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.75,0:09:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be a safety hazard during \Nthree-dimensional maneuver training.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll cut it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.35,0:09:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how long do you think it should be?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you wipe on me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.07,0:09:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My trust in others.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.98,0:10:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1\b1}This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bread!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was all I could save.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.97,0:10:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should have a drink of water first.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.91,0:10:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you God? Are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,God!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.96,0:10:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you two doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.12,0:10:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this girl has been \Nrunning all day until now.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.03,0:10:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think you're doing \Nthe right thing, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.37,0:11:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you doing it for potato girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was what you got out of it worth the effort?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.42,0:11:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.74,0:11:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, let's carry her to her bed.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you acting out of kindness too?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.10,0:11:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this to put her in my debt, \Nso I can take advantage of her.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can count on her stupidity.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.40,0:11:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First off, we'll test your aptitude!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.76,0:11:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those incapable of this aren't \Nsuited to even be used as decoys!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.31,0:11:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have you transferred to reclaimed land!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.77,0:11:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though this is but the most basic of tests,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.26,0:11:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can perceive one's aptitude for \Nthree-dimensional maneuvers at this point.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.85,0:11:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not wavering in the slightest.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.71,0:11:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She likely understands what \Nto do and how to do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1\b1}That's{\i0\b0} what I call aptitude.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appears we have a lot of talent this year.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.66,0:12:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, what about him?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.55,0:12:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's another example of aptitude.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.27,0:12:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you have the will, there can be \Ncases in which you greatly underperform.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Eren Jaeger?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.11,0:12:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Raise your upper body!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1\b1}What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1\b1}How am I supposed to...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.35,0:12:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1\b1}No way.
