Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.26,0:24:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,bears witness to mankind, \Nwhich has regained its dignity.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.97,0:24:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I can defeat the Titans."
